B.auO=new A.cw("What is the Tournament Calendar?","The Calendar tab shows upcoming live poker tournaments sourced from PokerNews \u2014 major series like WSOP, WPT, EPT, and regional events worldwide. Each listing shows dates, buy-in, guarantee, venue, and country.")
B.auB=new A.cw("How current is the tournament data?","The calendar refreshes automatically every Monday from PokerNews. Pull down on the Calendar screen to force a refresh at any time.")
B.auv=new A.cw("Can I filter by country?",'Yes. Tap the country filter chips below the app bar to narrow the list to a specific country. Tap "Show past" in the top-right to also display tournaments that have already ended.')
B.auN=new A.cw("Can I register or buy in through the app?","Not directly \u2014 TableLab is a tracking and study tool, not a registration platform. Each tournament card shows a link to the full PokerNews listing where registration details are available.")
